{"title":"记工手册","authors":["金哲"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":8,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"记工手册"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔朝鲜族〕金哲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夕阳染红田野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们踏上归程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用镐头和锄刃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在记工手册上写下了对党的忠诚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“大办粮食”的春雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振奋着我们的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的耳提面命的号召，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓舞我们叱咤风云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们在翡翠般的苗床里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提前创造出春天的奇迹；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们用快过闪电的速度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"栽下壮秧为好收成奠基。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！记工手册，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记满了公社社员的汗水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记满了新的劳动，新的收成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"显示着党的政策的胜利！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（紫荆译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}